<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2203] improved snowball testing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2203</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Snowball project has test vocabulary files for each language in their svn repository, along with expected output.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should use these tests to ensure all languages are working correctly, and it might be helpful in the future for identifying back breaks/changes if we ever want to upgrade snowball, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12445195">LUCENE-2203</key>
            <summary>improved snowball testing</summary>
                <type id="6" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/issuetypes/requirement.png">Test</type>
